title: Private  bathroom with private entrance
neighborhood: hercules, pinole, san pablo, el sob
posting_body: Nice size bright room with your own separate private entrance and bathroom.
New paint, new bathroom and new flooring.
It is located in a very nice safe location, convenient access to I-80/4 to San Francisco.
Carpool/bus directly nonstop to downtown SF in about 35 min.
Close to restaurants, shops and freeway.
Please tell some information about you and your contact phone number to view the place.
Easy access to Berkeley, downtown San Francisco, Berkeley, Concord, Pleasant Hill, Walnut Creek, Vallejo, and Fairfield.
Email your phone number, a little about you and your linkin links for quick response.
